code: static <R> Supplier<R> unchecked(CheckedSupplier<R> checkedSupplier) {     return () -> {         try {             return checkedSupplier.get().         } catch (Exception e) {             throw new RuntimeException(e).         }     }. }

static <R> CheckedSupplier<R> checked(Supplier<R> supplier) {     return () -> {         try {             return supplier.get().         } catch (RuntimeException e) {             throw new FlinkException(e).         }     }. }
